taints node prr lagya jata hai aur toleration pod prr lagaaya jata hai
taints lagane se koi bhi pod entry nhi lega uss node mein, whi pod entry le sakta hai uss node mein jisko uss taints ka toleration mila ho.

kubectl taint nodes node-name key=value:taint-effect ( PreferNoSchdule | NoExecute | NoSchdule)
kubectl taint nodes node1 app=blue:NoSchdule
toleration jo hoti hai vo define hoti pod k manifest file mein 
taint aur toleration pod ko ye nhi batte ki vo kha jayega , vo node ko baate hai ki tum kaise pod ko rakh sakte ho.
